entities.name: $degenai

entities.name: Soulgraph

entities.name: Jin

entities.name: jinintern

entities.name: Discord
entities.description: A communication platform used for community discussions and updates related to various projects, including ElizaOS.

entities.name: cwm

entities.name: cwm (Soulgraph)
entities.description: An individual or entity associated with Soulgraph, involved in a conflict with the ai16z team regarding token sales.

entities.name: ai16z DAO

entities.name: Solana

entities.name: ELI5

entities.name: plugin-autocoder

entities.name: GitHub

entities.name: plugin-knowledge

entities.name: eliza/eliza
